以去啲有信譽樓上舖配,平好多.<br />\n利申:無戴con,以上都係陪女朋友配con觀察得黎"},{"pid":"902bdcd2e661e514f046c571334952dde6416b17","tid":269814,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"荃灣有間平好多<br />\n樓下樓上都有大鋪<br />\n有曬機果堆"},{"pid":"58f2c427b003267ae075735c53a5a3bf47b0cb39","tid":269814,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"唔好上網買<br />\n一黎好多假<br />\n二黎你唔知自己隻眼咩「孤」度"},{"pid":"c2152dabfea4f89fbd350f5a146c35020797e8d1","tid":269814,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"帶錯同埋手勢除帶唔好有機會介損角膜<br />\n無散光2百頭有找"},{"pid":"93cb672ddb5014720662e83b9c3c45f0f2c6fc62","tid":269814,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你有冇散光</blockquote><br />\n兩年前配普通眼鏡散光得25<br />\n應該可以當無掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335f8d817eaee662a281a05a94484118177f4efd","tid":269814,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好上網買<br />\n一黎好多假<br />\n二黎你唔知自己隻眼咩「孤」度</blockquote><br />\n驗眼唔係會驗弧度架咩，點解會唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋包裝應該有寫？"},{"pid":"5b20eb06a15037815b2eba00d8479c14ad1b9cfe","tid":269814,"uid":70253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"配con都要開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次配con求其落間大鋪問喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻隻牌子唔同，唔同價錢<br />\n你配個陣佢會俾幾副你試"},{"pid":"7bd013f0871384b8b8a7e6d22d92499caa865d16","tid":269814,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴左好多年眼鏡想試下戴con<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要戴黎做運動，想配1day<br />\n想問下第一次去眼鏡鋪配大概預幾錢同搞幾耐，我住港島有無邊間平d?<img sr